See a problem?
Let us know!


  
  
            Established in 1911 in, Sixteen to One Mine is a mine where gold is found in highly concentrated deposits within the quartz vein. The mine has produced more than 1 million ounces of gold and is famous for its quartz and gold gemstone sought by jewelers. Sixteen to One Mine offers products, such as bracelets, earrings, pendants, and ladies and gents rings.
          






















